# Build context hygiene — keep the Docker daemon transfer small and prevent
# accidental inclusion of repo metadata or local agent state. The Dockerfile
# only COPYs explicit paths, so anything not listed here is already safe;
# this file just speeds up `docker build` by not shipping the rest.

# Repo metadata + CI
.git
.github
.gitignore
.beans
.beans.yml

# Local agent state (also gitignored)
.claude
.pi

# Docs that never go in the image
docs
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
README.md
SECURITY-NOTICE-TOKEN-ROTATION.md

# Local config that overrides config.example.js — never in image
js/config.js

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
